    Note over User, DB: 1. THE REQUEST PHASE
    User->>Pres: Sends Form Data (e.g., Email/Pass)
    Pres->>DTO: Validate Input (Zod Parse)
    DTO-->>Pres: Returns Validated Data Object
    Pres->>Service: Calls createUser(validData)
    
    Note over Service, DB: 2. LOGIC & DATA PHASE
    Service->>Service: Check Business Rules (e.g., "Is allowed?")
    Service->>Prisma: prisma.user.create(...)
    Prisma->>DB: SQL Query (Executed by Engine)
    DB-->>Prisma: Return Raw Data
    Prisma-->>Service: Return Typed Object (Prisma Model)
    
    Note over Service, Pres: 3. THE RESPONSE PHASE
    Service->>Service: (Optional) Filter Data (e.g., remove password)
    Service-->>Pres: Return Clean Object
    Pres-->>User: Return JSON / UI Update